Caladanie Wyndwalker<br>
Screaming Fist <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukrytogspiritwalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krytog Spiritwalker</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/16/01 4:37:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=151.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Icewell spell</span><hr size=1> Zen,<br>
   My apology if you felt my responses were directed at you and the specific issue at hand. As I had posted earlier there are two sides to every story. I find you to be a great guy, fair in dealing with people and have been a key person in leading raids. I by no means was intending to indicate you were wrong in your handling of the matter. My comments were meant to be general in scope and as means of potentially preventing misunderstandings. <br>
<br>
