<br>
    There is only one point I want to make here and that is this.  We don't need to bite each others heads off (figuratively speaking that is), we are supposed to be a group of people trying to work together... Zenkight no one said you did anything. It seems to me that Hareq is relating a story with the information he was given by another side.  Of course people in the SGA are going to have disagreements on things but we don't need to make the boards look like the blast furnace.<br>
<br>
    So all and all here's the question to ask yourself:<br>
<br>
DO MEMBERS OF THE SGA REALLY NEED TO FLAME EACH OTHER?<br>
<br>
